[Guest]: Yeah, so, you know, I mean, we're both there. And you know, I think we've got I think of

00:07:43.080 --> 00:07:48.280
[Guest]: this as an analogy from a different perspective. And bear with me because this goes weird.

00:07:48.280 --> 00:07:55.080
