[Amit Varma]: the Capital Mind podcast, then you that's an investment in yourself in subtle and unseen ways

03:47:42.360 --> 03:47:49.720
[Amit Varma]: it will pay off. So that's just sort of a fantastic piece of advice. And in that chapter, you then go

03:47:49.720 --> 03:47:54.920
[Amit Varma]: on to give such detailed advice that I, you know, I think people absolutely have to read it. One is

03:47:54.920 --> 03:48:00.360
[Amit Varma]: what you spoke about earlier about the importance of allocation, that think about allocation and it

