04:49:44.760 --> 04:49:51.400
[Guest]: The other guy says, no, it's a born innate skill. And they sort of make a bet is a bet of a dollar.

04:49:51.400 --> 04:49:56.760
[Guest]: And one guy says, I'll just pick a random guy off the street and I'll teach him how to win in

04:49:56.760 --> 04:50:02.280
[Guest]: the market. And he picks up this guy and you know, eventually it becomes very famous. He becomes a

04:50:02.280 --> 04:50:10.040
[Guest]: big stock market trader and the guy wins. There was a real actual world example of this, where

04:50:10.040 --> 04:50:15.800
[Guest]: there was a guy called Richard Dennis and another guy I forget his name. They had a bet that Richard

04:50:15.800 --> 04:50:22.360
[Guest]: Dennis said he could trade, he could train people to trade like they breed turtles in Singapore.

04:50:22.360 --> 04:50:29.400
[Guest]: So these people he hired, and he trained them were all called the turtles and all went on to make

04:50:29.400 --> 04:50:35.080
