04:50:35.080 --> 04:50:40.200
[Guest]: and, you know, probabilities and eventually you'll win if you just play enough. So he's found out the

04:50:40.200 --> 04:50:44.200
[Guest]: stock market is similar, you just play by the rules. So he found people who could play by the

04:50:44.200 --> 04:50:50.280
